OL,5, A report into allegations of bullying  
OL,6, against Scotland's first female bishop 
OL,7, has recommended she leave her role.    
OL,9,FThe report for the Scottish Episcopal  
OL,10,FChurch looked at allegations against   
OL,11,FBishop Anne Dyer in the Diocese of     
OL,12,FAberdeen and Orkney.                   
OL,14,FIt claims Bishop Dyer's diocese is     
OL,15,Fsuffering from "systemic dysfunction". 
OL,17,FBishop Dyer has responded by saying she
OL,18,Fhas faced "significant bullying and    
OL,19,Fharassment" since taking up the role in
OL,20,F2018.                                  
